QuestData.Title: Leave it to Mnemis
QuestData.Description:
I have deduced by the urgency in your collective voices that you wish to leave.
I will expedite your exit. There is a transport pad in the antechamber. I will ensure that the chamber is sealed once again on your exit.
Please accompany me.
QuestData.LogDescription: Use the Transport Pad in the Vault of the Archon.
QuestData.RewardText: We must hurry. The Archon must know what transpired here.
